*** Keywords ***
Reach Login
    New Browser    chromium    headless=True
    New Context    viewport={'width': 1280, 'height': 720}
    New Page     https://staging.callsight.tech/login
    Wait For Elements State    "Loading..."  hidden    timeout=150s

Attempt Login
